{"id":10062,"date":"2012-11-27T23:57:39","date_gmt":"2012-11-28T04:57:39","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.dailyhadithonline.com\/?p=10062"},"modified":"2023-09-01T12:48:08","modified_gmt":"2023-09-01T08:48:08","slug":"anfal-jihad-no-reward-for-booty","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/11\/27\/anfal-jihad-no-reward-for-booty\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Anfal: No reward for one who fights only for spoils"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Abu Huraira reported: A man said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, a man intends to fight for the sake of Allah, and he is seeking worldly gains.\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201c<strong>There is no reward for him<\/strong>.\u201d The people found that very difficult, so they said, \u201cReturn to the Messenger of Allah, for perhaps he did not understand you.\u201d The man returned, and he said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, a man intends to fight for the sake of Allah, and he is seeking worldly gain.\u201d The Messenger of Allah said, \u201c<strong>There is no reward for him<\/strong>.\u201d Then he returned a third time and the Messenger of Allah said, \u201c<strong>There is no reward for him.<\/strong>\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: <span class=\"il\">Musnad<\/span> Ah\u0323mad 7887<\/p>\n<p>Grade:\u00a0<strong><em>Sahih\u00a0<\/em><\/strong>(authentic) according to Ahmad Shakir<\/p>\n<p align=\"right\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0631\u064e\u062c\u064f\u0644\u064b\u0627 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u064a\u064e\u0627 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u064e\u0651\u062c\u064f\u0644\u064f \u064a\u064f\u0631\u0650\u064a\u062f\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062c\u0650\u0647\u064e\u0627\u062f\u064e \u0641\u0650\u064a \u0633\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0644\u0650 